  "description": [
    "12 ADVANCING WASHING TONS INTEREST STOCKS DULL II CLOSING SESSION Small Volumn of Trading Marks Todays Half Session By W 8 COUSINS Copyright IMS by Cosmopolitan CNewa Service NEW YORK Jan 20There was I aot much activity in the stock mar ket in todays half session Not only was there a smaller volume of transactions comparatively but also a considerable shrinkage in the number of active stocks appearing on the tape The market was in every respect a traders affair with a continuation of the tactics of the professionals in marking up their favorites Once again a sharp contrast was drawn between home and foreign developments our weekend reviews giving new evidences of the forward march of American trade and in dustry While foreign cables were weighted with apprehensive reports Os greater complications in the oc cupied German territory British and French exchange exhibited nerv ousness As a group the socalled mer cantile stocks were in good form today and a fairly heavy volume 1 was recorded in Macy CluettPea body May Department Stores Wool worth etc Macy was one of the leaders in the forward movement in the first hour advancing 3 points to 71 the highest recorded price"
